#. Tag: title
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Utilização"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:185
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The most common way to run <command>meinproc5</command> is simply as "
#| "<literallayout>\n"
#| "<userinput><command>meinproc5</command> <replaceable>docbook-file</"
#| "replaceable>\n"
#| "</userinput>\n"
#| "</literallayout> where <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable> is usually "
#| "index.docbook. This command creates &HTML; pages from the DocBook file. "
#| "Note that these pages are only viewable in &kde;-based browsers (like "
#| "&konqueror;)."
msgid ""
"The most common way to run <command>meinproc6</command> is simply as "
"<literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> <replaceable>docbook-file</"
"replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> where <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable> is usually "
"index.docbook. This command creates &HTML; pages from the DocBook file. Note "
"that these pages are only viewable in &kde;-based browsers (like "
"&konqueror;)."
msgstr ""
"A forma mais comum de executar o <command>meinproc5</command> é tão simples "
"como <literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc5</command> <replaceable>ficheiro-docbook</"
"replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout>, onde o <replaceable>ficheiro-docbook</replaceable> é "
"normalmente 'index.docbook'. Este comando cria páginas &HTML; a partir do "
"ficheiro DocBook. Lembre-se que estas páginas só são visíveis em navegadores "
"baseados no &kde; (como o &konqueror;)."

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:192
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you need to view the &HTML; output in another browser (for example, if "
#| "you're placing it on line), use <literallayout>\n"
#| "<userinput><command>meinproc5</command> --stylesheet "
#| "<replaceable>stylesheet-name</replaceable> <replaceable>docbook-file</"
#| "replaceable>\n"
#| "</userinput>\n"
#| "</literallayout> where <replaceable>stylesheet-name</replaceable> is the "
#| "full path to one of the &XSL; stylesheets in &lt;"
#| "kdoctools_installation_prefix&gt;/share/kf5/kdoctools/customization/. To "
#| "produce output suitable for the web, you can use <command>kde-web.xsl</"
#| "command> or <command>kde-chunk-online.xsl</command>. See the "
#| "<filename>README</filename> file in that directory for more details."
msgid ""
"If you need to view the &HTML; output in another browser (for example, if "
"you're placing it on line), use <literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> --stylesheet <replaceable>stylesheet-"
"name</replaceable> <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> where <replaceable>stylesheet-name</replaceable> is the "
"full path to one of the &XSL; stylesheets in &lt;"
"kdoctools_installation_prefix&gt;/share/kf5/kdoctools/customization/. To "
"produce output suitable for the web, you can use <command>kde-web.xsl</"
"command> or <command>kde-chunk-online.xsl</command>. See the "
"<filename>README</filename> file in that directory for more details."
msgstr ""
"Se precisar de ver o resultado em &HTML; noutro navegador (por exemplo, se o "
"quiser pôr 'online'), use <literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc5</command> --stylesheet <replaceable>nome-folha-"
"estilo</replaceable> <replaceable>ficheiro-docbook</replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout>, onde o <replaceable>nome-folha-estilo</replaceable> é a "
"localização completa de uma das folhas de estilo &XSL; em &lt;"
"prefixo_instalação_kdoctools&gt;/share/kf5/kdoctools/customization. Para "
"produzir um resultado adequado para a Web, poderá usar o <command>kde-web."
"xsl</command> ou o <command>kde-chunk-online.xsl</command>. Veja o ficheiro "
"<filename>README</filename> dessa pasta para mais detalhes."

